Evanson Asset Management, LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 12:59 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Evanson Asset Management, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Evanson Asset Management, LLC is an employee owned investment manager. It provides its services to individuals and their families, including high net worth individuals, and trusts. The firm manages separate client-focused portfolios. It invests in public equity, fixed income, and alternative investment markets across the globe. For its alternative investments, the firm invests in gold and commodities. It also invests in no-load stock and bond mutual funds which are passively managed. The firm obtains external research to make its investments. Evanson Asset Management, LLC was founded in 1995 and is based in Carmel, California.


